TT: dry bulb temperature at 2 meter above ground
Td: dew point temperature at 2 meter above ground
Tx: maximum of temperature for previous day
Tn: minimum of temperature for previous day
Tm: daily mean of temperature previous day
Tg: minimum temperature at 5 cm above ground last 12h
dd: mean wind direction during last 10 min. at 10 meters above ground
ff: mean wind speed during last 10 min. at 10 meters above ground
fx6: chance of maximum wind speed last 12 hours more than 45km/h
fx9: chance of maximum wind speed last 12 hours more than 75km/h
fx11: chance of maximum wind speed last 12 hours more than 100km/h
RR%6: chance of rain past last 6 hours
RR%12: chance of rain past last 12 hours
RR%24: chance of rain past last 24 hours
NL: cloud cover of low level clouds
NM: cloud cover of medium level clouds
NH: cloud cover of high level clouds
PPPP: pressure reduced to mean sea level
SS1: total time of sunshine during last hour
SS24: total time of sunshine past day
